        "en": "7.2 - What was the rationale for selecting this exact subset of electrodes?<div style='font-size: 70%; text-align:left;'><details> <summary> details </summary> <br>When you are making this decision, you may want to check out papers by Kriegskorte et al. (2009, https://doi.org/10.1038/nn.2303) or Gaspelin and Luck (2018, https://doi.org/10.1111/psyp.12639) on biases in time window and channel selection.</details></div>"
